Privacy Policy for MeloFlow MP3 App:

At MeloFlow, we are committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our MeloFlow MP3 App.

1. Information Collection:
   - MeloFlow MP3 App does not collect any personal information from users.
   - The app only accesses the MP3 music files stored on your device or in specified folders to provide playback functionality.
   - We do not collect or store any data related to your music library, playlists, or listening preferences.

2. Information Usage:
   - The MP3 music files accessed by the app are used solely for playback purposes within the MeloFlow MP3 App.
   - We do not use or share your music library data for any other purposes, such as advertising or marketing.

3. Information Security:
   - MeloFlow MP3 App is designed to operate locally on your device and does not transmit any data over the internet.
   - We implement reasonable security measures to protect the integrity of the app and the MP3 music files stored on your device.
   - We do not have access to or control over the security of the MP3 music files stored on your device.

4. Third-Party Services:
   - MeloFlow MP3 App may utilize third-party libraries or services for enhanced functionality, such as audio playback features.
   - Please note that the privacy practices of these third-party services are governed by their respective privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.

5. Children's Privacy:
   - MeloFlow MP3 App is not intended for use by children under the age of 13.
   - We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 years of age. If you believe that we may have inadvertently collected personal information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.

6. Changes to Privacy Policy:
   - We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time.
   - Any changes to the Privacy Policy will be reflected in the updated version of the app and will be effective immediately upon posting.

By using MeloFlow MP3 App, you consent to the collection and use of your information as outlined in this Privacy Policy. If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at finastratechnologies@gmail.com. 

Thank you for using MeloFlow MP3 App!
